title: MenOfWar [MAC OS X]
description:
This is Men Of War converted from windows with Wineskin, and is working perfectly.
Here are the system requirements for the game:

Minimum System Requirements
OS System: Mac OS X 10.6 Snow Leopard and Above
CPU: Intel Core 2 Duo 1.8Ghz
RAM: 1GB
GPU: Intel GMA X3100 128MB, GeForce 6200 (Radeon 9600) 128MB and Above.

Recommended System Requirements:
OS System: Mac OS X 10.7 Lion and Above
CPU: Intel Core 2 Duo 2.33GHz (Athlon X2 5000+)
RAM: 2GB
GPU: Intel HD Graphics 256MB or GeForce FX 8600 (Radeon HD2600) 256MB
